API Endpoints
Method  Endpoint          Purpose
GET/    api/health        Health check
GET/    api/schema        Retrieve full schema
GET/    api/{type}        List all entities of type
GET/    api/{type}/{id}   Get specific entity
POST/   api/{type}        Create new entity
DELETE/ api/{type}/{id}   Delete entity
GET/    api/search?q=     Full-text search
GET/    api/audit         Retrieve audit log

Entity Types: condition, intervention, assessment, resource, care_plan_template
